  The bamboo trees are getting new leaves and shedding the old ones. Looks like autumn, only in spring.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  竹林は新しい葉を伸ばし、古い葉を落としている。春なのに秋のようです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html">The bamboo trees are getting new leaves and shedding the old ones. Looks like autumn, only in spring.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08150.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08150.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Maple &amp;amp; Bamboo・もみじ&amp;amp;竹</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220513/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Maple &amp;amp; Bamboo・もみじ&amp;amp;竹" /><published>2022-05-13T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-13T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/maple-bamboo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220513/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Maple leaves in front of a bamboo grove, on a rainy day.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
雨の日、竹林の前のもみじ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html">Maple leaves in front of a bamboo grove, on a rainy day.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08141.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08141.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Yoshina・よし菜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220510/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Yoshina・よし菜" /><published>2022-05-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/yoshina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220510/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Late afternoon light hits the noren (curtain) of a restaurant in Kyoto&apos;s Pontocho district.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
京都・先斗町の料亭の暖簾を照らす昼下がりの光。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">Late afternoon light hits the noren (curtain) of a restaurant in Kyoto&apos;s Pontocho district.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5497.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5497.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tenryuji in the Afternoon・午後の天龍寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220506/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tenryuji in the Afternoon・午後の天龍寺" /><published>2022-05-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tenryuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220506/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The main hall and Sogenchi garden at Tenryuji Temple, lush green in the late afternoon.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
緑豊かな天龍寺の本堂と曹源池庭園。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">The main hall and Sogenchi garden at Tenryuji Temple, lush green in the late afternoon.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08079.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08079.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ruriko-in・瑠璃光院</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220505/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ruriko-in・瑠璃光院" /><published>2022-05-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/rurikoin</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220505/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
A popular &lt;a href=&quot;/191126&quot;&gt;spot for fall colors&lt;/a&gt;, Ruriko-in is a great place to experience the bright green leaves of late spring. Of course, everyone has to take a photo of their large polished gloss table reflecting the leaves outside. 
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  &lt;a href=&quot;/191126&quot;&gt;紅葉の名所&lt;/a&gt;所瑠璃光院は、晩春の鮮やかな青葉も見ることができます。
  
  外の葉を映し出す大きく磨き上げられたピカピカのテーブルは、誰もが写真に収めたくなるものです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">A popular spot for fall colors, Ruriko-in is a great place to experience the bright green leaves of late spring. Of course, everyone has to take a photo of their large polished gloss table reflecting the leaves outside.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08003.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08003.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Koi Nobori・鯉のぼり</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220504/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Koi Nobori・鯉のぼり" /><published>2022-05-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/koinobori</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220504/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 Carp-shaped windsocks fly in the breeze. These streamers, called &lt;em&gt;koi nobori&lt;/em&gt; are everywhere in Japan right now, displayed for Children’s Day, May 5th.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  風になびく鯉のぼり、「こどもの日」に飾られる。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><summary type="html">Carp-shaped windsocks fly in the breeze. These streamers, called koi nobori are everywhere in Japan right now, displayed for Children’s Day, May 5th.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5403.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_IMG_5403.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Golden Hills・金山</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220503/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Golden Hills・金山" /><published>2022-05-03T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-03T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/higashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220503/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 Looking across Kyoto at the hills of Higashiyama, filled with blooming golden  Itajii trees, from Senkoji Temple in Arashiyama.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の千光寺から、京都の向こうに金色のスダジイが咲き乱れる東山を臨む。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Looking across Kyoto at the hills of Higashiyama, filled with blooming golden Itajii trees, from Senkoji Temple in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R07986-green.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R07986-green.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Heavy Rain・大雨</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220429/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Heavy Rain・大雨" /><published>2022-04-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ame</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220429/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  It often rains in Kyoto, but heavy rain is rare. Today the rain was unusually strong, all day long. 
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  京都はよく雨が降りますが、大雨はめったにありません。今日は珍しく一日中強い雨が降っていた。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Rain" /><summary type="html">It often rains in Kyoto, but heavy rain is rare. Today the rain was unusually strong, all day long.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_IMG_5364.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_IMG_5364.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kasuga Taisha・春日大社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220428/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kasuga Taisha・春日大社" /><published>2022-04-28T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-28T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kasuga</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220428/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
